HTML & CSS framework
Version: 2.4.6
Author: Václav Vracovský (http://vracovsky.cz)
Date: February 2015


Requirements
______________________________________________________

nodeJs
http://nodejs.org/

Grunt
http://gruntjs.com/


Usage
______________________________________________________

1. Rename template folder under wp-content/themes and set the "templatename" in package.json (default: medio)

2. For development, run
$ npm install (only for the first time), then run
$ grunt
JS and CSS files are now watched and automatically compiled.

That's all.
